title: LF Team Jungle main/ top secondary role
body: Main jungle play most meta champs with some spicy techs. Would like to join a team for the OOL or a team for my university which is Curtin in Western Australia. Can practice almost every day bar weekend day time. Am serious and want to play with people who want to learn. Am currently gold 1 but soon to be plat 5

replies.body: Hey, my team has been having issues with our jungler not being able to practice with us as much as we would like, if you are interested you can join and play in a tournament on sunday March 12th with us, as of right now we have 2 silver and one platinum in our team, currently searching for jungle and adc/mid due to the reason mentioned above.
